This paper is about bug triage, which is a software engineering task. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a machine learning approach to improve the accuracy of bug triage, which falls under the scope of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses feature selection and instance selection techniques, which are related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and data mining (cs.SI).
